{"tid":1450951,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"冇走上前線既人麻煩都幫幫手","createTime":"2019-08-11T18:07:56.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-11T18:16:30.000Z","uid":260104,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"110777a890910a4921aeef31c90a2100188cf858","tid":1450951,"uid":260104,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T18:07:56.000Z","msg":"冇辦法走上前線既人可能有好多原因，但你地有一樣野真係可以幫到手。如果你身邊既人係同班狗有直接關係or係狗，請立即斷絕同佢地既關係。小朋友既，就要你既孩子同佢絕交，要佢地眾叛親離。<br />\n<br />\n可能我會比人屌話對錯focus，只係針對班狗。但佢地絕對係政府打壓市民既工具，咁就有必要打壓佢地，冇得手軟。"},{"pid":"d882e597c02d4978b8199ed33a5e7494d47d8849","tid":1450951,"uid":260104,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T18:08:06.000Z","msg":"自推"},{"pid":"89bd3842a81c464cebdd1e67988907bd1560687e","tid":1450951,"uid":260104,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T18:08:33.000Z","msg":"自推"},{"pid":"d2d5fc1c99258876804cbbd339055c0450064cb2","tid":1450951,"uid":37516,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T18:09:14.000Z","msg":"做<br />\n乜都做"},{"pid":"621c4592a6b995941dafdb51722338563a83979c","tid":1450951,"uid":2683,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T18:10:03.000Z","msg":"同狗有關既都要做"},{"pid":"e19d6ed1d95d29d4d51b50fdf86488dd1c78b20a","tid":1450951,"uid":260104,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T18:10:04.000Z","msg":"警察絕對要比社會孤立先"},{"pid":"21c6414131d4067dc5406554ddbd0c2ace79bf51","tid":1450951,"uid":43600,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T18:10:42.000Z","msg":"比埋data老豆搵仔"},{"pid":"cc7f0aa7c56f51a9fafcc16e7fb74b9abe8a9836","tid":1450951,"uid":260104,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T18:12:43.000Z","msg":"請各位手足幫忙，當佢地都受到好大壓力先唔會再亂黎。佢地不受監管，如果我地唔決絕咁做，前線既手足真係會好慘。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6eca0e9249dac6c9369a813249f9a6b48ca4e11f","tid":1450951,"uid":24612,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"